casebody.data:
Jeffrey WUNDERLICH, Respondent,
v.
Sharon WUNDERLICH; Respondent, National General Insurance Online, Inc., Appellant. WD 80685 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: March 6, 2018 John Mullen, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Christopher Harper, Kansas City, MO, Co-Counsel for Appellant. Spencer Farris, St. Louis, MO, Counsel for Respondent, Sharon Wunderlich. Jason Pottenger, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Respondent, Jeffrey Wunderlich. Before Division One: Thomas H. Newton, P.J., Victor C. Howard, and Cynthia L. Martin, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

National General Insurance Online, Inc. appeals a Jackson County Circuit Court judgment awarding $1.2 million in a personal-injury action in which it had unsuccessfully and repeatedly tried to intervene. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
